    <url>2019/11/21/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%9C%A8Android%20Studio%20XML%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<hr><h2 id="关于Android-Studio预设界面XML代码报错"><a href="#关于Android-Studio预设界面XML代码报错" class="headerlink" title=" 关于Android Studio预设界面XML代码报错"></a> 关于Android Studio预设界面XML代码报错</h2><h2 id="问题出现"><a href="#问题出现" class="headerlink" title="问题出现"></a>问题出现</h2><p>最近突然脑子一抽，买了本Kotlin的编程书来看，想尝试一下安卓编程，结果好不容易安装完，再仔细汉化一遍，AS就开始给我发抛<br><img src="en-resource://database/387:0" srcset="undefined" alt="f96742b8f8eb5b1ca8d60723c883860c.png"></p><h3 id="寻求办法"><a href="#寻求办法" class="headerlink" title="寻求办法"></a>寻求办法</h3><p>我就疯了一样开始寻找这个问题的解决方法，书查了，网也上了，找了3天终于找到这玩意<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/u013909053/article/details/101626021" target="_blank" rel="noopener">解决方案</a></p><h3 id="问题总结"><a href="#问题总结" class="headerlink" title="问题总结"></a>问题总结</h3><p>总的来说也不是什么大事，也就是我可能下了一个不知道哪里来的山寨版AS,<del>虽然还挺好用</del>，Gradle依赖不完全，本地的依赖库就这么点，导致编译器在检阅代码的时候发现了奇奇gaygay的引用，说到头来还是谷歌退出中国的锅。啥时候能回中国来啊。。中国苦百度久矣，Google play还不能用，中国网民属实水深火热，科学上网都找不到地方来。</p><h3 id="附上Gradle代码"><a href="#附上Gradle代码" class="headerlink" title="附上Gradle代码"></a>附上Gradle代码</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>&#123;</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    repositories &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        maven&#123; url&apos;http://maven.aliyun.com/nexus/content/groups/public/&apos;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        google()</span><br><span class="line">        jcenter()</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    dependencies &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        classpath &apos;com.android.tools.build:gradle:3.2.0&apos;</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">allprojects &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    repositories &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        maven&#123; url &apos;http://maven.aliyun.com/nexus/content/groups/public/&apos;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        google()</span><br><span class="line">        jcenter()</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">task clean(type: Delete) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    delete rootProject.buildDir</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后再一个Rebuild，重启AS就完事了</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
